# Performance Keyword (clouds-f)

Canonical source: `SKILL.md` in this skill root.

Apply this rule for `performance`, `slow`, `lag`, `Core Web Vitals`, `LCP`, `INP`, `CLS`, `bundle`, `rerender`, and latency optimization tasks.

## Performance Rules

1. Measure first, then optimize.
2. Prioritize proven bottlenecks over speculative cleanup.
3. Focus on render cost, bundle weight, waterfalls, and main-thread pressure.
4. Re-measure after each meaningful optimization.
5. Avoid regressions in accessibility and maintainability.

